#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.10.0/lua-api/core.md:589
msgid ""
"When shortcut call forms such as `ptool.run(cmdline, options)` or `ptool.run"
"(cmd, args, options)` are used, the per-call `options` table also accepts "
"`sudo`, `stdin`, and `trim` with the same meaning."
