#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.10.0/lua-api/core.md:698
msgid ""
"`stages` (table, required): Pipeline stage list. At least two stages are "
"required."
msgstr ""

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.10.0/lua-api/core.md:700
msgid "`options` (table, optional): Per-call overrides."
