msgstr ""

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.10.0/lua-api/core.md:714
msgid "`ok` (boolean): Whether every stage exited with status `0`."
msgstr ""

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.10.0/lua-api/core.md:715
msgid ""
"`code` (integer|nil): Summary status for the pipeline. On success this is "
"the last stage status. On failure this is the last non-zero stage status, or "
"`nil` if the relevant stage was terminated by a signal."
msgstr ""

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.10.0/lua-api/core.md:718
msgid "`codes` (integer|nil)[]: Per-stage exit statuses in stage order."
msgstr ""

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.10.0/lua-api/core.md:719
msgid ""
"`cmd` (string): Display form of the whole pipeline, such as ``printf hello | "
"tr a-z A-Z``."
msgstr ""

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.10.0/lua-api/core.md:721
msgid "`cwd` (string): Effective working directory used for the pipeline."
msgstr ""

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.10.0/lua-api/core.md:722
msgid ""
"`stdout` (string, optional): Present when `stdout = \"capture\"`. This "
"captures the stdout of the last stage."
msgstr ""

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.10.0/lua-api/core.md:724
msgid ""
"`stderr` (string, optional): Present when `stderr = \"capture\"`. This "
"combines stderr from all stages in stage order."
msgstr ""

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.10.0/lua-api/core.md:726
msgid ""
"`assert_ok(self)` (function): Raises the same structured `command_failed` "
"error shape as `ptool.run(...)` when any stage fails."
msgstr ""

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.10.0/lua-api/core.md:729
